Code preview of the table BC_租赁对象RS

drop table BC_RS cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: BC_RS */
/*==============================================================*/
create table BC_RS
(
RSID NUMBER(32) not null,
BCID NUMBER(32) not null,
"NewID" NUMBER(32),
"BoothCode" VARCHAR(20) not null,
"ParentID" NUMBER(32),
"RSCode" VARCHAR2(20) not null,
"RSType" INTEGER,
"FloorID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"ParentRSCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"NewestReallyArea" DECIMAL(20, 4) not null,
"NewestRSVectorArea" DECIMAL(20, 4) not null,
"NewestRSVectorInfo" BLOB not null,
"StartTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"EndTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
"SyncSAPflag" INTEGER default 0,
"StartDateInSAP" TIMESTAMP,
"IsNewRS" INTEGER,
constraint PK_BC_RS primary key (RSID)
);

comment on column BC_RS."Enable" is
'1：有效
0：无效';

comment on column BC_RS."SyncSAPflag" is
'0：未同步
1：已同步';

comment on column BC_RS."IsNewRS" is
'1：新RS
2：老RS';
